reviewText: I haven't had a lunch box since I was in grade school!  I love the gothic vampire design and it's fun to take to work!  It's a little smaller than I hoped, and my frozen lunches don't quite fit, but it's roomy enough for lots of other things.  Good quality, and delivered on time.
This lunch box arrived broken, and the description wasn't quite right. Got it on sale so it would have cost more to return.
